 PHOTOSHOP, CINEMA 4D<\/div><\/div><\/div><\/header><div class=\"t-box-b post-detail__body\"><nav class=\"post-detail__tabs\"><div class=\"post-detail__tab-dot is--active\"><\/div><ul class=\"post-detail__tab-list\"><div class=\"post-detail__tab is--active\">OVERVIEW<\/div><div class=\"post-detail__tab false\">CHALLENGE<\/div><div class=\"post-detail__tab false\">REFLECTION<\/div><div class=\"post-detail__tab false\">PROCESS<\/div><div class=\"post-detail__tab false\">AWARD<\/div><\/ul><\/nav><div class=\"post-detail__tab-body\"><ul class=\"post-detail__tab-body-list\"><div class=\"post-detail__tab-body-item is--active\">Celebrating 10 years of PINC and creating something special for an experience that has commemorated people from different cultures and backgrounds<\/div><div class=\"post-detail__tab-body-item false\">How to distinguish this decade of PINC compared to others? <br><\/div><div class=\"post-detail__tab-body-item false\">Even through 2 hurricanes, the team managed with online meetings to make PINC successful; to apply the feedback that was given from client<\/div><div class=\"post-detail__tab-body-item false\">Through trial and error of deciding style directions, we decided to keep it simple but have a sense of complexity: grain, light, and gradients (with additional colors to the palette)<\/div><div class=\"post-detail__tab-body-item false\">2025 ADDY Professional Silver Award (Elements of Advertising, Animation, Special Effects, or Motion Graphics)<\/div><\/ul><\/div><div class=\"post-detail__media-container\"><picture class=\"post-detail__media-image\"><source media=\"(max-width:600px)\" srcset=\"https:\/\/jasminegunarto.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/03\/OVERVIEW-scaled-1.webp\"\/><img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/jasminegunarto.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/03\/OVERVIEW-scaled-1.webp\" alt=\"\"\/><\/picture><picture class=\"post-detail__media-image\"><source media=\"(max-width:600px)\" srcset=\"https:\/\/jasminegunarto.com\/wp-content\/upl